Hello! My name is Sarah, and I represent RT 6 Boozers, your favorite local bar.

Hi Sarah! Nice to meet you.

It's nice to meet you too! Can I start by asking what your name is?

My name is John.

Thank you, John. How can I assist you today?

I was wondering about your happy hour specials.

Absolutely! Our happy hour runs from five PM to seven PM, and you can enjoy half price on select drinks.

Sounds great! Do I need to provide any personal information?

Yes, if you could provide your date of birth, we need to verify your age.

Sure, it's June sixth, nineteen eighty-five.

Thank you, John! One last thing, can you please confirm your phone number?

Of course! It's three zero three, five five five, one two three four.

Awesome! Thank you for that information. Is there anything else you would like to know?

No, that's all. Thank you for your help!

You're welcome, John! Thank you for your time, and we look forward to seeing you at RT 6 Boozers!
